title: House in Manor for Rent on September 1st
posting_body: I have a 3 Bed 2 bathroom house in Manor available for rent.
The house includes washer/dryer, stove, dishwasher, and refrigerator.
There is a detached garage that can fit 2 cars.
This house was previously rented to Tesla interns who commuted approximately 18 minutes to work.
I'm asking $2,500 which includes all utilities + internet.
